# AI Car Accident Detection System 🚗⚠️📍

An AI-powered system that detects car accidents using sensor data and sends live location alerts to emergency contacts and the nearest hospital.

## 🔧 Features
- Detects crashes based on speed & impact
- Sends SMS to:
  - Emergency contact
  - Nearby hospital
- Real-time GPS location
- Google Maps integration

## 🚀 Tech Stack
- Python
- GPS + Accelerometer sensors
- Twilio / Fast2SMS API
- Google Places API (for hospital search)

## 📦 How to Run
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python main.py

🚨 Accident Detected!
📍 Location: https://maps.google.com/?q=28.6139,77.2090
🏥 Nearest Hospital: AIIMS (1.5 km)
